==English==
===Etymology===
:from the Late Latin ''verbalis'', belonging to a [[word]].

===Adjective===
'''verbal'''

# of, or relating to [[word]]s
# concerned with the words, rather than the [[substance]] of a [[text]]
# consisting of words only
# expressly [[spoken]] or [[written]], as opposed to [[implied]].
# {{italbrac|grammar}} derived from, or having the nature of a [[verb]]
# {{italbrac|grammar}} used to form a verb

